e for any academic award or school appointment.\r\n\r\nCriteria for the award of a Scholar Badge.\r\n\r\nVI-VIII : Grade A1 (Marks range 91-100) Eng, Hindi, Maths, S. Science, Gen. Science.\r\nIX: Grade A1 (Marks range 91-100) Eng, IInd Lang., Maths, S. Science, Gen. Science\r\n\r\nThe final result will be decided according to the average marks obtained in two terms.\r\n\r\nResults declared at the close of the year are final and will not be reconsidered.','Admissions','','inherit','open','open','','8-revision-9','','','2013-06-17 10:30:47','2013-06-17 10:30:47','',8,'http://localhost/wordpress/8-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(127,1,'2013-06-17 10:31:07','2013-06-17 10:31:07','<span style=\"color: #800000;font-size: 20px; text-style: bold;\">Admissions</span>\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"color: #fff; border-left: 1px none #000000; border-right: 1px none #000000; border-top: 1px none #000000; border-bottom: 1px dotted #000000; background-color: #fff;\" align=\"left\" />\r\n\r\n<div style=\"width: 140px; height: 30px; background-color: #800000;\">\r\n<h4 style=\"color: #ffffff; text-align: center;\">Apply Online</h4>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<hr style=\"color: #fff; border-left: 1px none #000000; border-right: 1px none #000000; border-top: 1px none #000000; border-bottom: 1px dotted #000000; background-color: #fff;\" align=\"left\" />\r\n\r\nAdmissions to all the classes are ordinarily made in December and January for the academic year starting in April. However children are registered for all classes from November.\r\n\r\nAdmissions are made on the basis of merit.\r\n\r\nStudents coming from other schools should produce: -\r\n\r\nThe leaving/transfer certificate from the school last attended / bonafide certificate\r\n\r\nThe progress report of his/her academic performance and co-curricular activities in that school.\r\n\r\nThe original birth certificate &amp; a copy of the same.\r\n\r\nA calendar month’s notice in writing should be given by the parents before withdrawing a student fr